// these commands are to bind the hc-05 module to the obd port once the hc-05 has been put into AT mode

AT+RESET
AT+ORGL (Set to original)
AT+ROLE=1 (Set to Master)
AT+CMODE=0 (Set connect to a specific address)
AT+BIND=1234,56,789c72
AT+INIT (Need to connect)
AT+PAIR=1234,56,789c72,20 (20 means 20 second timeout)
AT+LINK=1234,56,789c72

// WHEN PUTTING IN AT MODE, DISCONNECT HC05 Voltage Wire while giving power to arduino.  Connect the voltage wire to hc05 once the code is uploaded.
